function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	if Hydra.ActorIsInPrefabScopedGroup(idActorSpawned, "SMP_Shaman") then
		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(idActorSpawned, RES_LOOP, idActorSpawned)
	else
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActorSpawned, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idActorSpawned, DEAD_ANIM)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false)
	end
end
